<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٠١١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/676">إِسْمَاعِيلُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5361">مَالِكٌ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5917">ابْنِ شِهَابٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4361">عُرْوَةَ بْنِ الزُّبَيْرِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a><span class="special">﵂</span>،<span class="c5"> زَوْجِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">«أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> صَلَّى، وَذَلِكَ فِي رَمَضَانَ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>